'''Daryne Joshua''' (wavutse 1992), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] <ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3736242/</ref>.  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''zamamaye cyane Noem My Skollie'' na ''Ellen: Die storie van Ellen Pakkies'' .  Usibye gukora firime, ni n'umugiraneza, umwanditsi, uwashushanyije animasiyo, uwashushanyije amajwi, itangazamakuru n'umuyobozi ushinzwe itumanaho.<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/daryne-joshua/</ref><ref>https://www.screenafrica.com/2017/02/15/film/film-content/film-director-speak-daryne-joshua/</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye kandi akurira i Cape Town. Yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Livingstone. Ni umwarimu kuri Sinema n’Ubushakashatsi bwa Sinema muri Cape Peninsula, Kaminuza y’ikoranabuhanga<ref>https://www.f6s.com/darynejoshua</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka irindwi, yatangiye gukina muri filimi ngufi . Muri kiriya gihe, yakoze no kugurisha imigani mu inshuti ze muri Bridgetown.  Nyuma yaje kwiga muri AFDA, Ishuri ryubukungu bwo guhanga no kubona impamyabumenyi itandukanye<ref>http://www.spla.pro/index.php?page_inc=fiche&type=personnes&no=51044</ref>. Niwe washinze, umwanditsi akaba n'umuyobozi wa Gambit Films yashinze akimara kurangiza. Gambit Films yakoze ikinamico ya mbere ya Afrikaans ya Cape Town, ''Suidooster'' ica kuri DSTV na Kyknet<ref>https://www.tribute.ca/people/daryne-joshua/58785/</ref>.  

Muri 2016, yayoboye filime ye ya mbere ''Noem My Skollie'' . Filime yatoranijwe nkuwinjiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 89 bya Academy<ref>http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-no2017067630</ref> .  Iyi filime yatsindiye ibihembo bya RapidLion kubera amashusho meza na Filime nziza yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo muri 2017. Intsinzi ya firime, yakoze film ye ya kabiri yerekana ''Ellen: Die storie van Ellen Pakkies''<ref>https://letterboxd.com/director/daryne-joshua/</ref> . Byari bishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo ya Ellen Pakkies<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/daryne-joshua/51044</ref>. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam (IFFR) ku ya 27 Mutarama 2018 kandi ryishimiwe cyane.    Yasohotse muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo ku ya 7 Nzeri 2018<ref>https://www.programme-tv.net/biographie/513039-joshua-daryne/</ref>. Muri 2018, yanditse inyandiko ya firime ngufi ''nimero 37'' iyobowe na Nosipho Dumisa . Inyandiko yaje gutsindira igihembo cya Afurika yepfo Filime na Televiziyo (SAFTA)<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1686178-daryne-joshua</ref><ref>https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Daryne-Joshua%2C-dir.-Call-Me-Thief-%5BNoem-My-Jacobs/cb8b964133279b78d32bd8d292001d1894709dd6</ref>. 

